ShimeLinux is an unofficial Linux port/Kotlin rewrite of Shimeji-ee by Kilkakon
(https://kilkakon.com/shimeji). The project also incorporates work from Shimeji
by Yuki Yamada of Group Finity, hqx-java by Arcnor and FlatLaf by FormDev.

